OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FEarly
OL,6,Fshowers will die out during the
OL,7,Fevening to leave a largely dry night.
OL,8,FSome clear intervals, although low
OL,9,Fcloud, and some mist and fog patches
OL,10,Fare likely to form.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FEarly low cloud and mist
OL,13,Fwill soon lift to leave a fine day
OL,14,Facross the region. Skies brightening
OL,15,Fup through the afternoon to leave
OL,16,Fplenty of sunshine. Turning cloudier
OL,17,Fovernight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
