OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FOvernight rain should gradually clear
OL,7,Fon Thursday to leave some sunshine for
OL,8,Fthe afternoon. Largely dry and settled
OL,9,Fthereafter too, and starting to feel
OL,10,Fwarmer again in the sunshine.
